Isolectotype of 
<taxonomicName id="4C6492B4FFBDC837FE52F984FD05251F" authority="Arv." authorityName="Arv." box="[413,702,1537,1558]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Hieracium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="7" pageNumber="208" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cataractarum">
<emphasis id="B9103525FFBDC837FE52F984FD35251F" box="[413,654,1537,1558]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="208">Hieracium cataractarum</emphasis>
Arv.
</taxonomicName>
-Touv. &amp; Huter in BM (barcode BM001050678).—Image by courtesy of The Natural History Museum, London (Herbarium BM), reproduced with permission.
